      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "CONCILIATE (4) was well in the betting here last week but it all went wrong, breaking early and locking wheels. Came from this barrier for a 4m fourth at Menangle prior so is capable of much better. BUBBA NAY (10) switches to the Seaton Grima yard from Queensland where he was a winner at Albion Park last month. Can measure right up. D J ROCK NZ (7) has been racing well from similar draws to this. Scored a 1.7m win at this circuit and distance two back then dropped back to the mile for a 3m third last week. Major player. IRE OF THE DRAGON (5) is hard to knock having placed in both outings since coming from a similar draw to this for a tough win at this venue.",
